<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَلَقَدْ خَلَقْنَا فَوْقَكُمْ سَبْعَ طَرَائِقَ , وَمَا كُنَّا عَنِ الْخَلْقِ غَافِلِينَ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٩٩:</span> قَالَ ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ: <span class="c3">{سَبْعَ طَرَائِقَ}</span>: سَبْعَ سَمَوَاتٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
